data.description: Escape the ordinary and step into tranquility with this exceptional country oasis nestled in Springtown, TX! Embrace the beauty of nature on a 2.65-acre corner lot adorned with lush trees that provide shade and privacy. Inside, discover a thoughtfully designed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven that's perfect for country living. The converted garage has been transformed into a versatile bonus room, ideal for a home office, media room, 4th bedroom or even a fitness space – the possibilities are endless! The grand stone fireplace and hearth in the living room add warmth and charm. The large pantry mudroom and additional storage area are convenient, and the fenced-in garden with rich soil is a great feature for those who enjoy gardening and producing their own vegetables. Step out to your own private paradise as you make a splash in the refreshing pool, the ultimate remedy for those warm Texas days.
